cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses neural machine translation models. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with improving the performance of machine translation models. It may also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks for machine translation. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with improving the accuracy of translation.
